{"tid":1486014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"機場一定要繼續入！824機場見！","createTime":"2019-08-18T17:45:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T15:47:28.000Z","uid":52609,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9cd5d55dd0c88213742a10be8f05bf890424a32c","tid":1486014,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:45:05.000Z","msg":"812 用狼來了，恐嚇和理非即刻離開機場<br />\n813 用鬼捉鬼方式，想令和理非同勇武割蓆。防暴唔敢入T1暴力清場，只係T1外捉人<br />\n814 機場禁制令，想令和理非唔敢入<br />\n<br />\n接連三招出得咁快<br />\n證明中共真係好驚我地去機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更加驚和理非同勇武團結，不割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n818證明完我地不割蓆，我地下一步就要入返機場再玩過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n機場812係兩個月嚟其中一場打得最漂亮嘅勝仗！<br />\n繼續大大力錫香港機場春袋！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［ 8 2 4 召 集 ］ 機  場  交  通  壓  力  測  試<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1483611\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1483611</a><br />\n<br />\n我地係空管主任同機師，阻大家少少時間，請大家聽我地講幾句<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1478911\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1478911</a><br />\n<br />\n[行動POST] 前機場貨運員工有野講！塞爆機場攻略同討論集中貼<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1451867\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1451867</a><br />\n<br />\n貨運撚教路空運黃金8小時先係政府經濟死穴<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1457587\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1457587</a><br />\n<br />\n機場拆櫃朋友向我報夢點燒中共春袋<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463854\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463854</a>"},{"pid":"7d3eb2be434fef7d474888fdfde078d4a9236b77","tid":1486014,"uid":52609,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:46:26.000Z","msg":"唔好塞s1 s52 s64<br />\n<br />\n好多人返工放工靠佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf3c42706712cf7ed0136c19375182702759e3d6","tid":1486014,"uid":275435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:47:46.000Z","msg":"留名先！<br />\n-<br />\n【818】重新定義咩係「香港腳」！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1485466\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1485466</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"209933bd0824c6915cf338e575d46a7f637e05a3","tid":1486014,"uid":86649,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:01:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R4UOpJv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR4UOpJv.jpg&h=62b96872&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1202a133c42b28189fe017064ff713de44578619","tid":1486014,"uid":13935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:02:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d1fd8b833a4de65fa3a47fbc4976a113b31c60b","tid":1486014,"uid":47555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:02:44.000Z","msg":"唔好意思！<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />阻阻大家想問吓：<br />\n<br />\n參觀青馬大橋有咩要注意？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1486009\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1486009</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"34ff45594c3cd9576d4c03b5249e71060eb9c4b9","tid":1486014,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d1fd8b833a4de65fa3a47fbc4976a113b31c60b","tid":1486014,"uid":47555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:02:44.000Z","msg":"唔好意思！<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />阻阻大家想問吓：<br />\n<br />\n參觀青馬大橋有咩要注意？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1486009\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1486009</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"